      • AnnotatedTypeVariableImpl

        public AnnotatedTypeVariableImpl(TypeVariable<?> type,
                                 Annotation[] annotations,
                                 AnnotatedType... annotatedBoundaries)
        Create a AnnotatedTypeVariableImpl from a TypeVariable Any user-supplied annotated boundaries override the associated boundaries from type when specified.
        Parameters:
        type - TypeVariable to annotated
        annotations - Annotations indicating annotations on type
        annotatedBoundaries - user-supplied AnnotatedTypes indicating the boundaries, overriding from type. null entries indicate no override for the relevant boundary
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException -
        • When type is null
        • When type.getAnnotatedBounds() is invalid
        • When annotations contains a null
        • When annotatedBoundaries specifies an annotated type that does not match the respective boundary on type
        See Also:
        AnnotatedTypeVariableImpl(TypeVariable)
